data.description: This beautifully updated, immaculately maintained condo features a private wooded setting.  The interior has recently been professionally painted and features two spacious bedrooms, both with walk-in closets, 2 1/2 baths that have been remodeled. The master bath features new granite and tile.  The Family bath has new tile and vanity.  Separate front foyer entrance, formal Living Room, Kitchen with snack bar, newer ceramic splash guard, two pantry's, new fixtures, and built-in appliances.  Dining area with new lighting fixture leads through sliding glass doors to a private patio and wooded view.  The foyer, hall, kitchen and dining area have newer wood composite flooring.  Divided full basement.  One car carport and one guest parking space.
